{"tid":518563,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"[台測][粵語][睇住高達砌模型]Gundam 0083 星塵回憶","createTime":"2018-01-03T13:07:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T13:35:53.000Z","uid":52796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e541c31223f5d43b7b5e490b9801d747cc982422","tid":518563,"uid":52796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:07:36.000Z","msg":"機動戰士高達0083：星塵回憶錄<br />\n<img src=\"https://gss1.bdstatic.com/9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy/baike/w=400/sign=54c021478bcb39dbc1c06656e01709a7/cefc1e178a82b901c394869e798da9773912ef66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgss1.bdstatic.com%2F9vo3dSag_xI4khGkpoWK1HF6hhy%2Fbaike%2Fw%3D400%2Fsign%3D54c021478bcb39dbc1c06656e01709a7%2Fcefc1e178a82b901c394869e798da9773912ef66.jpg&h=c4e66710&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一年戰爭完結後三年，基於地球聯邦軍重建計劃而被提議的「高達開發計劃」開始執行，其中兩台原型機RX-78GP01與RX-78GP02A為了進行性能測試而搬運至澳大利亞&amp;quot;特林頓&amp;quot;基地。吉恩殘黨查知此項計劃，於是襲擊基地企圖奪取裝載有核彈的GP02A。曾經被稱為「所羅門的惡夢」的吉翁軍王牌駕駛員阿納貝爾&middot;賈圖少校成功的搭上了GP02A，但是在企圖脫離的GP02A面前，新手測試駕駛員浦木宏駕駛了GP01攔阻，揭開了宇宙世紀0083年迪拉茲紛爭的序幕。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/manonroad\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fmanonroad&d=Wopcp%2FV0PR%2FWj2kd24BNmBOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=a264fe66\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/manonroad</a>"},{"pid":"4438720064260ef6bd89e4ad1cddbf2fc5b23111","tid":518563,"uid":52796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:25:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01711579f9ab41236d010d8ac1993b8bb440e7ed","tid":518563,"uid":52796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T13:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4facaabbe624ae17dcc27037a2eef640b0265f9","tid":518563,"uid":52796,"like":0,"